quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  93,1,"M wẽen ne sõore!"
  93,2,"La ne yʋngã t'a sã n wa ligi."
  93,3,"Fo Soabã pa bas-fo, A pa kisg-fo."
  93,4,"Lɑ Yaoolmã lɑ sõma ne foom n yɩɩd Rãeenmã."
  93,5,"La yɩ bilfu, fo Soabã na wa n kõ-f tɩ f yardẽ."
  93,6,"A pa mik foo tɩ f yaa kɩɩb t'A mobg-fo?"
  93,7,"La A mik foo tɩ f yaa Menemda, t'A kãndg-fo?"
  93,8,"La A leb n mik foo tɩ f yaa talga, t'A sek-fo?"
  93,9,"Rall sã n yaa ne kɩɩba, ra modg-a ye."
  93,10,"La sã n yaa ne bõosa, bɩ f ra tãs-a ye."
  93,11,"La sã n yaa ne f Soabã neema wã, bɩ f yẽse."
